    dc:description "Figure 13. Orthonychia sp., with openly coiled larval shell; Mississippian (Chesterian) Imo Formation, Arkansas, USA. (A) SNSB-BSPG 2023 I 89. (A 1) Apertural view. (A 2) Lateral view. (A 3) Oblique lateral view on openly coiled protoconch. (B) SNSB-BSPG 2023 I 90. (B 1) Lateral view. (B 2) Detail initial bulb of protoconch. (B 3) Apertural view. (B 4) Apical view. (B 5) Oblique lateral view." ;
